    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (tmp + ((v1 + 0.42 - v0 + 0.79) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.04)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.56) / (tmp + 0.20 / v2 + 0.26)) / ((tmp + 0.65 - tmp + 0.98) / (v2 + 0.48 / v1 + 0.66)))
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (tmp + v0)
    tmp = wp.sin(v1)
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.66 * v2 + 0.89) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.87)) + (v1 - 0.14))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
